Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統剛剛走進司法部大樓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Vice President just entered the Department of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現場請到的是艾拉·薩伊德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're here with Ayla Sayyad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她發表在《華爾街電訊報》上的文章\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whose Wall Street Telegraph article
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接促成了這次調查  艾拉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}catalyzed the investigation. Ayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵問題在於\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The issue at stake is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮是否也在某種程度上捲入其中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whether the White House was in any way involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否有國外資金用於換取政治支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was foreign money traded for political favors?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是否對外交關係產生影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did it influence diplomatic relations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單是為來自中國的政治獻金洗白就是違法的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just the act of laundering Chinese contributions is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這筆錢對白宮決策產生影響的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If it had a significant impact on White House policy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是更嚴重的罪行了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that's a far more serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾多次與丹尼爾·拉尼根會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've met with Daniel Lanagin on multiple occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  2003年起我們曾11次共處一室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We were in the same room, yes, on 11 occasions since 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其中我們交談過的只有三次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we only spoke on three of those occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幾次已經標出來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those instances are highlighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們談了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did you discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那都是在籌款會上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, these were fundraisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對著幾十號人發表演講\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I speak to dozens of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼特定的話題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}usually about nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是南方人  鄧巴女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm southern, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽教導我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My mother taught me that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席間講話不僅禮貌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}conversation during mealtime is not only polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有助消化\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it aids the digestive process.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你沒有跟他談到過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you didn't speak to him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿道希部落向這些超級政治行動委員會捐款的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about the Adohi tribe's contributions to any of these super PACs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從不和支持者提超級政治行動委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I never discuss super PACs with any supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們熟悉法律規定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We both know the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這些禮節性的談話中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}During one of these polite conversations,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根先生可曾向你提起過馮山德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}do you recall Mr. Lanagin ever mentioning Xander Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說過這個名字嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does that name mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說除了鋪天蓋地的媒體報道嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Other than being plastered all over the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個角度說  就像我也聽說過金·卡戴珊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In that regard it means as much as Kim Kardashian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我再說得明確些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then let me be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對馮先生涉及政治的活動有多少瞭解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What knowledge do you have of Mr. Feng's political activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你丈夫的意思還是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this coming from your husband, or is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}From me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是說我不再支援法案了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it's not that I don't support the bill anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是採訪的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's just the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經答應讓馬特做專訪了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've promised Matt an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那往後推幾周吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe in a few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等調查塵埃落定之後再說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}once the investigation has died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《紐約時代雜誌》可不會乾等著我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The New York Times isn't going to wait for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經騰出十月份的封面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They've already scheduled the cover for October.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑑於我們的安排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Based on our timing --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就恕難參與了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I can't be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為嘉樂威的事  是不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the Galloway nonsense, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾  別這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你直說就行  我們是朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can say so. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確影響不好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會真相信我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't actually believe I --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但國內還是有不少人信的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But enough of the country still does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特現在需要爭取每一份支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Garrett needs every bit of support he can get right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你心意已決了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So there's no convincing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會儘可能幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll help as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地幫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有傳言說你和馮先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are rumors that you and Mr. Feng
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在去年五月的貿易峰會上進行了私下接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}served as back channels to the trade summit last May.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是"傳言"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Exactly. Rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,峰會期間馮就在美國境內\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have Feng in the U.S. during the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他做了私下接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, if he was back-channeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and even if I were aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種外交接觸一般都是保密的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}any form of diplomatic communication is usually classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和總統說起過馮嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you ever discussed Feng with the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北京每一個權勢人物我們都會說起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any major player in Beijing is worthy of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是承認了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So that's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是陳述一般情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a general comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在能源危機期間與別人說起過他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you discuss him during the energy crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你是指跟他合資投資精煉廠的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I assuming you're alluding to the refinery co-venture with --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我是指雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. With Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們從來沒聊起過精煉廠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The refinery was never part of our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要的是能立即見效的方案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We needed an immediate solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建精煉廠在短期內什麼都解決不了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A refinery would have solved nothing in the short term.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且據我所知  這交易最後黃了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it's my understanding that deal fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但塔斯克拿到了補貼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Correct. But Tusk did receive a subsidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他核電供應商也都拿到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As did every other nuclear energy provider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他和馮有聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But his connection with Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有釤補貼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then a subsidy on samarium --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人從這筆補貼中獲利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody made any profits off these subsidies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至多也就是保本而已\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At best they were breaking even.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  雷蒙德一開始還拒絕接受補貼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In fact, Raymond fought us on the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們再說說傑斐遜港大橋吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then let's back up to the Port Jefferson Bridge.
