Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也怨不得她  這的確值得擔憂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't blame her. It's a valid concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我不會談嘉樂威的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell him I won't engage on Galloway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以乾脆也別問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so there's no point in asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是馬特·貝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is Matt Bai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要問什麼我們說了不算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't dictate what he'll ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他肯定會問這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he will ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就說我不會迴應這些無聊八卦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, then I'll just say I won't answer tabloid questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個合理的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a legitimate question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醜聞對選舉有什麼影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How the scandal could affect the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建議我們也不做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I say you pull out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取消掉整篇專題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We scrap the whole piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬在和我們對著幹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jackie is fighting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統方面又指望不上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The leadership is noncommittal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要這篇專訪讓大家重新關注法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need this article to refocus attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這於你不利啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it'll hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你的形象和法案都不利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Both your personal image and the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們誰都不靠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if we cut the cord,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好的兩場採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we schedule two interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼取消了  馬特不會生氣嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then we cancel, won't Matt be furious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家只會看到我們的退縮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The story will be about pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要權衡利弊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're talking about the lesser of two evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你成為目標\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want you to become the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使我們的努力白費\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to undo all the work --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我去呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then what if it's not me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你說第一夫人不打算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you said the first lady wasn't going --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是她  是其他人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not her. Someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建設大橋是否是換取切斷共和黨資助金的籌碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was the bridge a trade-off to prevent additional GOP funding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As far as I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座大橋是總統在兌現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the bridge was a delivery on a promise
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對選民做出的承諾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the president had made to the voters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒問完嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are we finished here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會見過多少位國會議員  鄧巴女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many members of Congress have you interviewed, Ms. Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}About 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,194位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}194.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I want to be of help,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想前面194位都已經說得差不多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I doubt I can offer any more than the 194 that preceded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了一些有用的證詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have gotten some useful testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從誰那兒得來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾議院高層\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A high-ranking House member.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導層的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not at liberty to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃·博奇  傑姬·夏普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bob Birch? Jackie Sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人說他參加了7月14日\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This individual says he attended a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在總統辦公室的會議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}July 14th in the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說是個男的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She said "He,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一定是博奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so it must have been Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德肯定能輕易收買他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure Raymond had no trouble buying him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也參加了那次會議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You attended that meeting also.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是這樣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得那次會議的主題嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you recall the subject of that meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一波共和黨的攻擊廣告\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A wave of conservative attack ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有足夠財力與之抗衡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We were being outspent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很震驚吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It must have been quite a shock
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根轉而把錢捐給了另一黨派\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when Lanagin's tribe shifted contributions to the other party,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前他們從沒給共和黨捐過錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when they hadn't given a single dime to the Republicans before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這的確會令我們震驚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it would have been a shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們當時並不知道錢是哪來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we didn't know where the money was coming from at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我的線人說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}According to my source...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃·博奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bob Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的線人說  當時預計有兩千五百萬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My source says the estimate was 25 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引用你說的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said, and I quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"憑空出現這麼多錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"With this kind of influx,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有人違規了"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you can be sure somebody isn't playing by the rules."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是我說過的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sounds like something I might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃的記性比我好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bob has a better memory than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑斐遜港大橋剛獲批\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The money stopped just after
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這筆錢就中斷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the Port Jefferson Bridge was approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是真有想法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there a theory here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是查不出頭緒就瞎猜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or are you just grasping at straws?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大橋與馮有關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The bridge leads to Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮與拉尼根和塔斯克有關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feng gives me Lanagin and Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克和總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk and the president --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴女士  你想玩六度分隔的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Dunbar, you want to play six degrees of separation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能扯上{\u1}吉米·霍法{\u0}和教皇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you could throw in Jimmy Hoffa and the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}82年神祕失蹤的工會領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一度分隔如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then how about one degree of separation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格拉斯·斯坦普  你的幕僚長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Douglas Stamper, your chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是7月14日他在拉尼根的賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is him at Lanagin's casino July 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用這些申請了搜查證  調出了飛行記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I used these to get a warrant for flight records.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  斯坦普先生飛去北京\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The next day, Mr. Stamper was on a flight to Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼去賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why was he at the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼去北京\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And why was he in Beijing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想與委託人談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would like to speak to my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不拖泥帶水\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I keep things simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道重要的是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know what my priorities are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是有這麼個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But there's this -- this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不在我的生活中  而是在我生活的邊緣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's not even in my life, except on the edges,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以界限很模糊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}making things blurrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這並不讓我想喝酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It doesn't tempt me to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那感覺更像...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's more like she --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她給我的感覺就像我喝酒時的感覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's more like she feels what it was like when I was drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是無法滿足\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I couldn't get enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我喝多少酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No matter how many drinks I had,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是喝不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和她在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I don't want to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說  我想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, I -- I -- I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她更像是我女兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's more like she's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者我母親\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道了  太亂了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know. This is fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該再跟她聯繫了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should cut her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像戒酒一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The way I did with booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些  說完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's all. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你與我們分享\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要一些時間回答你的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll need some time before responding to your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意等\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I could wait as long as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能要花上一段時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It could take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關國家安全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are national security matters at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統需要諮詢顧問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vice president needs to consult with his advisors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國家安全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}National security?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真要用這招嗎  奧利弗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you really gonna play that card, Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的回答可能涉及保密資訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His answers could entail classified material.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麼時候能得到迴應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When can we expect a response?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會通知你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以拿走這些截屏照片嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}May we hold onto the screen cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請便\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會儘快聯繫你  鄧巴女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll be in touch soon, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要覺得我們在針對你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you think you're insulated, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們調查的不止道格拉斯·斯坦普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our investigation is much bigger than Douglas Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就到這兒吧  鄧巴女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's enough, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你的時間  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your time, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Happy to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛出虎口  又入狼窩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}From the lion's den to a pack of wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是滴血的肉  那就殺了別人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you're fresh meat, kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給他們更新鮮的肉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and throw them something fresher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是菲茨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, I'm Fitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道  你可以自己硬挺著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you know, uh, you can isolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨自承擔這一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}white-knuckle this shit if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者你也可以向他人求助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or you can ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有擔保人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Got a sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  都已經14年了  我很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's been 14 years. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話在背面  如果你改主意的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Number's on the back, if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你有司機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thought you had a driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望他聽到什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't want him overhearing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不該來這個州\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't even be near this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去加州繞了點遠路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Long layover on my way to California.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稽核員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got auditors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和聯邦探員都在我辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}federal agents in my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢視每一份檔案和檔案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}going through every file, every document.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們連我的垃圾都翻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're going through my god damn trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她傳喚你就堅持保持沉默\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just stick to the Fifth if she subpoenas you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼知道去查斯坦普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, how do they know to look for Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,專查那天的錄影\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To search the tapes on that exact day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂下結論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是要犧牲我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're throwing me under the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德才是對頭  你不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Underwood's the roadkill. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要搞垮我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're going to fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會找到辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你已經預見到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的家人會得到妥善安置\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you and your family will be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經給我提供認罪條件了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're already offering me a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒被起訴呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You haven't even been charged yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我合作的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能少坐幾年牢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll do less time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的家人會一無所有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but your family will have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你出來他們還是一無所有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll still have nothing when you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你作證指認雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You testify against Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還是不會有事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and he'll still walk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們只有你的證詞作證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because all they'll have is your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而現在你的證詞沒多少可信度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that doesn't count for much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要是不害怕你就不會來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't be here if he wasn't afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來不是因為他害怕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not here because he's afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你害怕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm here because you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要確定你不會做蠢事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I want to make sure you don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在反覆和北京溝通後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}After repeated conversations with Beijing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們堅持他們的立場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they remain intractable in their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今早命令一個航母戰鬥群\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This morning I gave orders for a carrier group
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沖繩海域重新部署\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to reposition near Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們的艦隻不會直接\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This won't put our ships in direct confrontation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和中國軍艦對峙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with the Chinese vessels,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但又能把對方納入航母空襲範圍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it will put them within reach of airstrikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天晚些時候會知會中國大使\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be informing the Chinese ambassador later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會和五角大樓聯合發表聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll release a statement in coordination with the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的釤儲量\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, our stockpiles of samarium
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最多能再堅持兩個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}will only last another two months at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we go this route --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道所有人的擔憂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I've -- I've heard everyone's concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this is the decision I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行的怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有些問題需要後續澄清\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have a few follow-up questions that we have to address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼要緊的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, nothing major.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是零七碎八  一點細節\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just odds and ends. A few details.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為這調查會簡短而溫和\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was under the impression this would be short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也以為  但她不依不饒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So was I, but she's very deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事得儘快平息  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need this over, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少白宮需要這事儘快過去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At least as far as the White House is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能分心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't be distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是局勢如此緊張的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not with warships on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確信馬上就會結束了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm confident we're in the home stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去不像嘴上說得那麼輕鬆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you seem more concerned than you're letting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搓手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're fidgeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的畢業戒指\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's my class ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I forget I --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把它埋了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I buried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說來話長了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- it's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過你這麼緊張  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never seen you this stressed before, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過你這麼疲憊  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I've never seen you this tired before, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也有自己的圈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've got rings of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑眼圈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dark ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越發明顯了  是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, they're getting worse, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該在總統辦公室的沙發上多打打盹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should take more naps on those sofas in the Oval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今光打盹可管不了用了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, naps don't cut it these days, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都解不了乏\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not even a dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謊話連篇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lie after lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先是對檢察官  現在是對總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}First to a prosecutor, then to a president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到我全無防護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I feel exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我手指上曾被戒指庇護的面板\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like the skin where my ring used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強如阿喀琉斯  也終被踵上一箭斃命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even Achilles was only as strong as his heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他老不接電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's not answering his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去參加互助會了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He went to a meeting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的去幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the middle of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在可能在往回趕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think he's on his way back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要他趕緊回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want him back now as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  這是給你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, this arrived for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雷米跳槽去格蘭頓-希爾時你送給他的手錶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The watch you gave Remy when he left for Glendon Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從手錶背面的名言認出來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I recognized it from the quote on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他留資訊了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was there a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  只有這隻表\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Just the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊聯繫道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's find Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不介意塑料杯子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Forgive the plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呂克·圖伊曼斯  他有真本事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Luc Tuymans. He's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就信你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll take your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的  這些全都不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not mine. None of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在加州  你要是想賣房子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}California, you want to sell your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的房屋中介會先裝修一番\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}your realtor decorates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起碼會裝個樣板間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, one room at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算搬到哪去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where you moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在索諾瑪有座小農場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I have a little ranch in Sonoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子離開了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My wife's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子也不和我說話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My kids won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我還有我的畫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But at least I'll have my painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還畫畫嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不畫  農場也是胡扯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. And there's no ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其餘的話  其餘的都是真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But the rest of it -- the rest of it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為傑奎琳·夏普而來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm here about Jacqueline Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在考慮僱用她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're thinking of hiring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做說客嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A lobbyist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能贏不了連任競選了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She could lose her re-elect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在局勢對在位者不利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not a great time to be an incumbent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你和她關係很近\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you two are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來是想要什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, you're looking for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推薦函嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是K街員工流動率最低的一家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have the lowest turnover of any shop on K Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}K街上有很多智囊公司  遊說公司和倡導團體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是有原因的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在給格蘭頓-希爾物色什麼樣的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you looking for at Glendon Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心狠手辣  爭強好勝的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A killer instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你找她算是找對人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, she certainly has that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Forgive me if I'm prying,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是她造成了你的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but did she have anything to do with your, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Departure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬做了她必須做的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jackie did what she had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠不會原諒她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll never forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我理解她為什麼要這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I understand why she did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她究竟做了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用現金買的票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I paid cash for my ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常謹慎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯然不夠謹慎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Clearly not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  賭場裡到處是攝像頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, the casino had cameras everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本無法避開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There was no way to avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們的監控錄影肯定有幾千小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But there had to have been thousands of hours of footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼找出來的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now how they found that --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個問題我必須要問  道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to ask you a question, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  但你要如實作答\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'm sorry, but I need you to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是又開始酗酒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}God no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Truly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想都沒想過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近的表現可很像喝醉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it would explain a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完全有權生氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have every right to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經顧不上生氣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm more concerned than I'm upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在需要你  道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need you now, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常需要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我都不年輕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失敗  都會老死在牢裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we fail, we'll die in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近不在狀態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't been myself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你14年前也是這麼說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's what you said to me 14 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給了你第二次機會  也收穫了回報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I gave you a second chance, it paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你戒酒了  道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You got clean, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份工作是我最看重的  先生  無比重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing means more to me than this job, sir. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道你能搞定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to know that it can be managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要我的幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you need my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會伸出援手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能自己解決的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局面會好轉的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Things'll be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒給過別人第三次機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never given someone a third chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我再給你一次機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Until this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常感激\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你後悔的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請相信這一點  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please believe that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雷米讓他們找到錄影的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was Remy who alerted them to the footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是他的離職禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His going-away gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀讀背面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Read the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他想傳達什麼資訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think he's trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到他  給我安排一次會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but track him down and set up a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴那邊怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒法逃開事實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't run from the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我說什麼  我就說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll say whatever you want me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我負全責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll take responsibility for all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能會起訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She could indict you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚就是做這個的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's what having a staff is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個更好的解決辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have a better solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們一起承擔責任    -怎麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We'll both take responsibility.   - How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後天和鄧巴安排一次會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Set up an interview with Dunbar. Day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們倆需要時間做足準備    -是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You and I need time to do our homework.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼時候弄的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆幫我修好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Meechum helped me fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們不讓我跑步  我總得想辦法健身\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If they're not gonna let me run, I have to work out some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把它搬上樓了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You carried it all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更隱祕  有人幫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For privacy. I had help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-密查姆    -沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Meechum.   - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還真是樣樣通\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, he's a jack of all trades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-工匠  搬傢俱的    -肉盾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Handyman. Furniture mover.   - Human shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們有證據證明道格出現在不該出現的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They have evidence of Doug being where he shouldn't have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講實話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你該不會真打算...    -不是全部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You're not actually gonna --   - Selectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過絆了一下  還沒摔倒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a stumble, not a fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是絆一下  你不會這個樣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You aren't like this when it's just a stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼樣子    -你害怕了  我看得出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Like how?   - You're scared. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1分39秒劃五百米  這是我的最佳成績\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}500 meters at 1:39. That was my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此為目標吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shoot for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}墮胎等於謀殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}墮胎傷害女性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}丟人  通姦者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-藥挺有用的    -那就好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- The meds are helping.   - Oh, that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街角那些人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those people at the end of the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬧得挺厲害\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一天到晚不消停  週末人數還翻番\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're there 24/7. Twice as many on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在都習慣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're so used to it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能脫鞋嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I take off my shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得該穿得正式點  但我真不喜歡高跟鞋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought I should dress up, but I am not good with heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  當然可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽說和裙子很搭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My mom said they went with the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道過去六個月很難熬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know the last six months have been difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要你的幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒能像預想的那樣得到領導層的支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We just don't have the support that we expected in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也猜到你不會只是想問問我的近況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I figured this wasn't just about checking up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前改過主意  我理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You changed your mind before, and I understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在你的情況似乎穩定多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But now it seems as though things are more stable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you willing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都坐在你家了  說不有點過意不去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's hard to say no when I'm in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也聽到了外頭那些人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you hear those people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們聲音很響  但我們要發出更高的聲音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're loud, but I think we need to be louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這聲音不能是我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it can't be my voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經是嬰兒殺手  和出軌者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because I'm the baby killer, the cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音得是你發出的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It needs to be your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你沒有汙點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A clear voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在軍事法庭上作證了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm already testifying at the court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡不對媒體開放\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that's closed to the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事曾發生在很多人身上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are so many people this has happened to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一定是我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是你打來了電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because you're the one who called.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算在麥金尼斯判刑之前發表嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna try to put it out before McGinnis gets sentenced?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯  有空嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth? You have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬特  我一會兒打給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Matt, I have to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統錄用你的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When the vice president brought you on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是反對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I advised against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不得不承認你幹得很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I can't deny you've done a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I appreciate you saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很注重保護副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm very protective of the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很難跟旁人分擔這份職責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I find it hard to share that duty with anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也導致我可能出錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which leaves me open to error.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的缺點之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's one of my faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我跟副總統說的那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As I told the vice president,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道信任需要我自己爭取\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand that trust is something that I need to earn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我得到工作的途徑不正\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And given how I got the job --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果副總統信任你  那我就信任你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the vice president trusts you, then I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在是一個團隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're a team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也沒法孤軍奮戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the truth is I can't do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我做任何事都行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything and everything you ask of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能與媒體無關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It might have nothing to do with the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新聞發言人不過是個名號\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Press Secretary is just a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有兩個任務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have two tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先  給我找到雷米·丹頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}First, find me Remy Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要小心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But be discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會找到他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其次  我要你去翻閱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Second, I need you to go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統的行程記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}through the Vice President's travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去十年的所有記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything in the past 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要找什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何軟肋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything that could hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從前往後找\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll work forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從後往前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You work backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去辦  還有道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm on it. And Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}刪除瑞秋?  刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.49,0:24:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南茜  幫我訂部新手機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nancy, I need you to order me a new phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.26,0:25:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}追蹤道格拉斯·斯坦普  刪除聯繫人瑞秋  手機追蹤中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.78,0:25:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說是"零七碎八""馬上就會結束"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said "Odds and ends." The "Home stretch."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.42,0:25:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幾個小時前才看到了這些內容\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was presented with this information just hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.62,0:25:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是能招致彈劾的罪行  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're talking about impeachable offenses, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.27,0:25:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不會  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not at all, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.20,0:25:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的幕僚長...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your Chief of Staff was --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.23,0:25:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時覺得賭場跟這事有關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had a gut feeling that the casino was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.07,0:25:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我派道格去查了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I sent Doug down there to get to the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.78,0:25:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一發現聯繫就該馬上去找司法部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should have taken this to the DOJ the first inkling you had --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時就不想那麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's exactly what I didn't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.07,0:25:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一沒有什麼  我卻製造事端\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To create some ruckus if nothing was going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.15,0:25:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能私自調查  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't go on conducting your own investigations, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.12,0:25:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查明真相  盡職調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fact-finding, due diligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.59,0:25:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.17,0:25:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有任何違法行為  我必須知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If any laws were being broken, I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.65,0:25:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就要這麼跟鄧巴說嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's what you want to tell Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.79,0:25:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不透露我們的外交手段\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That I didn't want to disclose our diplomatic protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.19,0:25:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心中期選舉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That I was concerned about the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:25:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想保護美國總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that I wanted to protect the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.77,0:25:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我做得不對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, maybe what I did was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.59,0:26:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒幹任何違法的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I didn't do anything illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.40,0:26:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You certain of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.08,0:26:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟我的律師認真探討過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've discussed this at length with my lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.26,0:26:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我們承認這一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dunbar does not strike me as the sort of person
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.05,0:26:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得鄧巴也不會就此打住\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who will put on the brakes, even if we admit all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.26,0:26:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而還可能促使她繼續深挖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In fact, it might encourage her to dig deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.65,0:26:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.88,0:26:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算上交我全部的行程記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is why I want to hand over all of my travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.91,0:26:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你也該這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I think you should, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自願上交嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Volunteer them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.25,0:26:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  表示我們樂意合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. As a gesture of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.83,0:26:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們表示做得夠多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Haven't we made enough gestures?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.48,0:26:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣她就不會那麼叫勁了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That'll take the wind outta her sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.00,0:26:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不想讓她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I don't, uh, want her,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.18,0:26:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細檢視我所有的行蹤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}uh, poring over every one of my comings and goings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.11,0:26:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在擔心他的婚姻諮詢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's worried about his marriage counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.67,0:26:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也該擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as he should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.37,0:26:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是在擔心你的婚姻諮詢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're worried about your marriage counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.00,0:26:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被外界知道  會造成多大影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Imagine the fallout if the public were to find out that --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.81,0:26:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是大海里的一根針\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A needle in a haystack,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.75,0:26:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是鄧巴要找的那根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and not a needle that Dunbar is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.58,0:26:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經會見了一半的國會議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's interviewed half of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女人是要見血\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That woman's after blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.75,0:26:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是八卦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But not for gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.04,0:26:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算她真的起疑了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And even if she does raise an eyebrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.69,0:26:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是去探望一位生病的朋友  不是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you were visiting a sick friend, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  表面上是這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, ostensibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.67,0:26:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這她沒什麼可說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, she couldn't possibly find any fault with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.95,0:27:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫嘉利克過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like Galich in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.21,0:27:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不打擾了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let you two talk privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.65,0:27:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候去見鄧巴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When are you seeing Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.00,0:27:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天  這樣你也有時間準備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow, so you have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟比爾談談  回頭找你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll speak to Bill and get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.05,0:27:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會建議你不要這麼做  是他職責所在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'll advise you against it, which is his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.80,0:27:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我會強烈建議你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I would just encourage you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.82,0:27:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想政治而不是法律\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to think politics and not legalese.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.85,0:27:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.27,0:27:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議員女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.38,0:27:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要投票給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why should I vote for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.10,0:27:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  馬克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's -- it's okay, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.40,0:27:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.56,0:27:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來很疲憊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.09,0:27:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忙了一天競選嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Long day on the campaign trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.32,0:27:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒跟我說過哈維梅耶女兒的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You never told me about Havemeyer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.15,0:27:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everyone knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The whole world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.32,0:27:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道你常去探望她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But not that you visited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.32,0:27:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是你洩露出去的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That you leaked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.00,0:27:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大老遠跑來加州就是為了問我這些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You came all the way to California to ask me about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.04,0:28:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是到了加州才知道的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I came to California to find out about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.12,0:28:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提出買下哈維梅耶的房子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I offered to buy Havemeyer's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.66,0:28:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他就那麼告訴我了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but he told me for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.36,0:28:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.79,0:28:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實忙了一天競選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has been a long day on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.87,0:28:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不相上下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's still a close race.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.40,0:28:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是選民知道你是怎麼當上黨鞭就不會了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But not if the voters know how you became whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.50,0:28:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在威脅我嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you honestly threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.99,0:28:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安排和弗蘭克的會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Set up a meeting with Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.97,0:28:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎你怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't care what you talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.86,0:28:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你單獨一人  會面也有記錄就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}long as you're alone and the meeting is on the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.90,0:28:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你去和鄧巴談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then you're gonna sit down with Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.42,0:28:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經問完我了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've already done my interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.70,0:28:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她  是弗蘭克逼你那麼說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell her Frank grilled you on your testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.73,0:28:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作偽證嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perjure myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.97,0:28:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保住你的位子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Save your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.06,0:28:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說出去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know what? Tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.44,0:28:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想那會有什麼後果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Think how that'd play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.21,0:28:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.31,0:28:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真要為了弗蘭克毀了自己嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'd really toss yourself off a cliff for Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.14,0:28:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不效忠於弗蘭克·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have zero allegiance for Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.92,0:28:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會受他操縱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't be manipulated by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.56,0:28:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更不會被你操縱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I sure as fuck won't be manipulated by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.95,0:28:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是虛張聲勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.44,0:28:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.41,0:28:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.26,0:29:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不在乎我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How little I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.42,0:29:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那跟這個沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.63,0:29:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has everything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.83,0:29:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該覺得噁心  但我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should feel disgusted, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.26,0:29:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是特別失望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just supremely disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.82,0:29:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們十分鐘前接到電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We got the call 10 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.87,0:29:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接從白宮顧問那裡打來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Direct from the White House counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.44,0:29:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統要上交一切嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The President's turning over everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.84,0:29:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從他就職那天開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}From the day he took office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.93,0:29:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會包括他去拜訪那位朋友嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we're sure this includes the visits to his friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.66,0:29:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  安保人員全部出動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has to. It was full security detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.11,0:29:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Phenomenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.07,0:29:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有下手的地方了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have something we can work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.78,0:29:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於我的記錄...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, as for my logs...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.10,0:29:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.28,0:29:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿生命打包票嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'd bet your life on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.02,0:29:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.98,0:29:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Me, too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.31,0:29:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經檢查了兩次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've been through 'em twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.27,0:29:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反複檢查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}backward and forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.34,0:29:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲明呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.52,0:29:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的收件箱裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In your inbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看過了  塞斯幹得很漂亮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I looked it over. Seth did a nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.32,0:30:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會面一結束我們就要把訊息釋出出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to go wide with this the moment the interview's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.19,0:30:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣鄧巴如果打算釋出什麼訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so that we beat Dunbar to the punch
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.49,0:30:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以先發制人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in case she decides to release something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.25,0:30:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會守在電腦前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be at my computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.99,0:30:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一收到道格的訊息就按下"發送"鍵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}ready to press "Send" the moment I hear from Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.81,0:30:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆睡過覺嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have either of you slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.02,0:30:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很清醒  全速運轉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're awake. Fully operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.43,0:30:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去洗個澡  換件衣服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You take a shower and put on a fresh suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.60,0:30:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生  我們在那邊見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. I'll see you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.40,0:30:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有至少三小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have at least three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.57,0:30:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打個盹吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.28,0:30:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在我辦公室睡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can use my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你作證的時候麥金尼斯將軍就在法庭裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}General McGinnis was in the courtroom when you testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.08,0:30:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.50,0:30:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你私下見過他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Had you seen him in person --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.52,0:30:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他侵犯你之後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, since he assaulted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.25,0:30:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.79,0:30:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼感覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So what was that like?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.16,0:30:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愉快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.23,0:30:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼個不愉快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not fun how?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.17,0:30:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難受  真的很難受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was hard. Really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.23,0:30:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.84,0:30:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意把文章的焦點轉移到你身上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I agreed to change the focus of my piece to focus on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.27,0:30:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道這肯定很難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and, you know, I know this has gotta be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.21,0:31:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你得幫幫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need you to help me out a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.31,0:31:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.32,0:31:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很擅長這個  我很緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not very good at this. I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.93,0:31:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打電話去安德伍德夫人的訪談時挺好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You seemed fine when you called into Mrs. Underwood's interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.34,0:31:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在電話那頭跟我在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She was there with me on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.74,0:31:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的緊張情緒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.10,0:31:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自從你被侵犯後  這一直是個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know that's been an issue since the assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.64,0:31:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種防禦心理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The defense brought up
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.43,0:31:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引起了情緒與精神的不穩定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what they called emotional and mental instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.45,0:31:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's what always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.78,0:31:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被攻擊的人會再次被攻擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The person who was attacked gets attacked all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.40,0:31:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼感覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How did that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.93,0:31:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得憤怒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It made me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.70,0:31:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律師一直問我恐慌症的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The lawyer kept coming after me about my panic attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.41,0:31:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我的抗抑鬱藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my antidepressants.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.39,0:31:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我只是緊緊盯著麥金尼斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I just kept staring at McGinnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.69,0:31:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他知道我能承受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted him to see I could take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.60,0:31:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很堅強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That I was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.67,0:31:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他先轉過臉去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to make him look away first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.49,0:31:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  當聽到我說他不只是侵犯我的身體\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. When I said he did more than violate my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.53,0:31:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還背叛了自己的國家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He betrayed his country.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.59,0:31:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀了海軍陸戰隊的聲譽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He robbed it of a good Marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.42,0:31:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們談談國會正在談論的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's talk about the Sexual Assault Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.86,0:31:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性侵法案吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that's in front of Congress right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.06,0:31:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人提出了很強烈的反對意見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know it's taken some significant opposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.20,0:32:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是另一個老兵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}most notably from another veteran,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.99,0:32:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑奎琳·夏普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jacqueline Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.53,0:32:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我說  她也背叛了自己的國家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you ask me, she's betraying her country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.17,0:32:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.56,0:32:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.21,0:32:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你多給我們幾天時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for giving us a few extra days.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.14,0:32:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心對我來說不是問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no problem being patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.14,0:32:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能因此得到坦率的回答\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as long as it leads to forthright answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.15,0:32:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你繼續等待了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I won't make you wait a moment longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.48,0:32:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以開始了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.92,0:32:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找到這裡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.97,0:32:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.54,0:32:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就完事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're just finishing up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.79,0:32:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think, Mr. Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.68,0:32:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著還是剃了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keep growing it or have it shaved?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是留著吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ah, I guess I'll keep growing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.11,0:32:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.89,0:32:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把後面清理一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me just clean up the back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.20,0:32:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了  麥克  讓我們單獨待會兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, Mack, if you'd give me a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.34,0:32:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.02,0:32:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概十年前我在這裡建造了這個地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had this place built down here about 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.97,0:32:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我厭倦了每兩週都要開車穿過整個城市\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got tired of driving all the way across town every two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.72,0:32:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在坐個電梯就到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now it's just an elevator ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.48,0:32:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真方便\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.56,0:32:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道不方便的是什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know what isn't convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.25,0:33:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我辦公室裡擠下八個律師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cramming eight attorneys into my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.19,0:33:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡不是為召集我律所所有合夥人準備的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was not designed for the entire partnership of my law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.17,0:33:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們比較擔心拉尼根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're worried about Lanagin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.23,0:33:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有點害怕  但他能挺住\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's a little shaky, but he'll hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.43,0:33:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.47,0:33:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博奇出手了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Birch delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.65,0:33:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴提出斯坦普的問題了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And did Dunbar bring up Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.77,0:33:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會面是閉門的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The sessions are closed-door,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.06,0:33:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想她肯定會提的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I can't imagine she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.52,0:33:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可憐的哈維梅耶那邊呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what about poor Havemeyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.07,0:33:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在傑姬·夏普的事上對我們有幫助嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was he any help to us on Jackie Sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.14,0:33:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的猶豫說明進展不順吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do not take your hesitation as a promising sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.91,0:33:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向來不喜歡讓你失望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I never like disappointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.94,0:33:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他什麼都不知道嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.10,0:33:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.58,0:33:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他是確實不知道呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, do you think that's because there's nothing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.13,0:33:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是他在保護她呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or because he's protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.73,0:33:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.58,0:33:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再找一個別的議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can go to another congressman --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.64,0:33:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.68,0:33:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須是個曝光率高的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has to be somebody high-profile,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.69,0:33:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導層的人  才能引起轟動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}someone in the leadership who will make waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.32,0:33:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我再找找博奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me get back to Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.38,0:34:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太明顯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Too obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.01,0:34:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然他擺明瞭不會對弗蘭克手軟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}now that he's shown no sympathy for Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.07,0:34:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算盤不能打得太響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This can't look orchestrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.19,0:34:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多線作戰  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Multiple fronts, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.29,0:34:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須得是傑姬·夏普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Has to be Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.00,0:34:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mack?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.04,0:34:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把頭髮弄完吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's finish up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.13,0:34:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去幹活兒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I gotta get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.33,0:34:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  老闆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You got it, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.30,0:34:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也得去幹活兒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need to get back to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.61,0:34:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說過的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what we discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.17,0:34:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它們辦成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.60,0:34:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前否認你是去私下接觸的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You denied being a back channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.07,0:34:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒否認\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did not deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.27,0:34:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有證實  因為這是機密資訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I chose not to confirm because it was classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.35,0:34:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的辦公室一直否認\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But your office has consistently denied --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.93,0:34:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓道格那麼做的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I instructed Doug to do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.11,0:34:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我的新聞部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}along with my communications department.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.16,0:34:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私下接觸如果公之於眾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When a back channel becomes public,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.03,0:34:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就沒什麼用了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it defeats its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.35,0:34:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精心編造的謊言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An orchestrated deception --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.73,0:34:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們不予置評\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we had refused to comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.05,0:34:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們就會知道確有其事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it would have suggested that it was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會危及這一渠道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which would have endangered the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.22,0:34:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在沒辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I really had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.38,0:34:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮先生目前在迪拜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Feng is currently in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.07,0:34:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.62,0:34:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他因腐敗指控畏罪潛逃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's fleeing corruption charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.75,0:34:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是他第一次被指控了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not the first time he's been accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.61,0:34:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的問題是什麼呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.18,0:34:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是他洗錢  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know he laundered the money, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.78,0:34:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到確鑿證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's just a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.90,0:34:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是遲早的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before I have the proof to substantiate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.49,0:35:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我的問題就是  我再問一遍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So my question, which I am asking again,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.81,0:35:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當時是否知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is whether you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.10,0:35:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再回答一遍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I will repeat my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.78,0:35:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時並不知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.01,0:35:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時的確覺得有點不對勁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did sense that something was awry,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.28,0:35:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格知道我的擔憂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and Doug was aware of my concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得調查清楚是我的責任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I took it upon myself to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.45,0:35:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統並不知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vice president didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.91,0:35:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道他去賭場的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You had no knowledge he was going to the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.05,0:35:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但這並不代表\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}None. But that doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.51,0:35:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不對我手下的行為負責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't take full responsibility for my staff's behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.65,0:35:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我責無旁貸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The buck stops with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.76,0:35:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你發現了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.02,0:35:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒發現  沒有非法行為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing. No illegal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.28,0:35:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不像你那麼神通廣大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't have the same resources that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.84,0:35:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有所懷疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you suspected,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.74,0:35:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不立即聯絡國家印第安人博彩委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}why didn't you go immediately to the NIGC,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.02,0:35:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,印第安人事務局  或者...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the BIA, the Department --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.34,0:35:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.32,0:35:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們中期選舉很吃力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're facing very difficult midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.29,0:35:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想為一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to bring attention
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.39,0:35:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實據的判斷而引發關注\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to a series of allegations that may have no basis in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.26,0:35:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許這邏輯不是很合理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, that may have been misguided logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.07,0:35:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我當時的選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but that's how I chose to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.48,0:35:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯誤全在我一個人頭上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The mistake is mine and mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.81,0:35:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟道格沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not Doug's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.48,0:35:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然更算不到總統頭上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And certainly not the president's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.88,0:35:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是說我覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It shouldn't surprise you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.74,0:35:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒看到事情的全部  你不會意外吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if I say it feels like I am not getting the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.13,0:35:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算把全部展示給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is why I'm prepared to give you the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.71,0:35:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧利弗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.15,0:36:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮相信透明度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The White House believes in transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.65,0:36:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統全部個人出行記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All of the vice president's personal travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.65,0:36:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還包括我十年黨鞭任期內的記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the last 10 years since I became whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.33,0:36:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和總統就職後的所有記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As well as the president's since inauguration.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.03,0:36:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會面的物件和時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There should be no doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.30,0:36:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有任何問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as to whom we met with and when.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.57,0:36:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很懷疑裡面的內容\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am skeptical about what this contains.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.14,0:36:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點我們也預料到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is what we anticipated
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.59,0:36:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以奧利弗會全程在場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and why Oliver will walk you through anything
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.83,0:36:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪你審查全部材料\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you might need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.99,0:36:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都在那兒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.13,0:36:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你還有其他疑問或要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if you have any questions or requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.04,0:36:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也願意傾力協助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we'll be happy to facilitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.76,0:36:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始我很緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, at first I was really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.99,0:36:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一進入狀態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But then as soon as I started getting into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.24,0:36:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始吐露心聲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}starting speaking from my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.79,0:36:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都自然脫口而出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}all these things poured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.40,0:36:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些我一度想說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.86,0:36:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想說的都說出來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That I've been wanting to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.73,0:36:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯告訴我馬特很滿意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth told me that Matt was very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.04,0:36:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想做更多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.03,0:36:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做更多採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More interviews?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.11,0:36:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報刊採訪  上電視\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Articles. TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼都可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.89,0:36:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.79,0:36:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很好  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's great, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.55,0:37:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你給我這個機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for making me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.29,0:37:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對我來說是邁了一大步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was a big step for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.39,0:37:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還要趕飛機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have a plane to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要我做別的採訪  我可以留下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can stay longer, if you need me to do another.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.84,0:37:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你先回芝加哥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why don't you head back to Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.47,0:37:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我們制定好計劃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and as soon as we put a plan together
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.45,0:37:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再給你打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we can give you a buzz?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.95,0:37:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能喝杯水嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I get a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.55,0:37:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自來水  還是瓶裝的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tap is fine, or you want bottled --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.11,0:37:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漢納希女士的車準備好了  夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've got Ms. Hennessey's car ready, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.07,0:37:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Edward?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.22,0:37:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去機場接她時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did she seem all right
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.16,0:37:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when you picked her up from the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.82,0:37:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.52,0:37:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定  正常嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.83,0:37:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  可以這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.16,0:37:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她情緒起伏很大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's very up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.78,0:37:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反覆無常  容易激動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Very skittish and manic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.30,0:37:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她確實有點緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I guess she did seem nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.01,0:37:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒怎麼交流\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We didn't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.19,0:37:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面等\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.54,0:37:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Megan?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.17,0:38:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.75,0:38:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.68,0:38:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.01,0:38:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車在外面等著了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The car is ready whenever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.70,0:38:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.82,0:38:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have a safe flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.72,0:38:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.86,0:39:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與鄧巴女士的談話卓有成效\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just had a very productive interview with Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.98,0:39:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發新聞稿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Send out the press release.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.16,0:39:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.90,0:39:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎  夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You okay, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.77,0:39:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  我只是打碎了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm fine. I just dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.34,0:39:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.47,0:39:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我可以的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, uh, it's fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.93,0:39:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我來  你光著腳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I've got it. You're barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.24,0:39:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華  你真的不需要這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Edward, you don't have to. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.16,0:39:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天  怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.16,0:39:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.47,0:39:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找繃帶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me get some bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.69,0:39:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.46,0:39:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我堅持  別動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I want to. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.96,0:39:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前的報導都是正面的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The coverage has been mostly positive so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.15,0:39:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴那邊呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dunbar's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.60,0:39:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只說很期待對記錄的稽覈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All they've said is they look forward to reviewing the logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.01,0:39:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人提到道格嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any heat on Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.44,0:39:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.37,0:39:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人要求我發表評論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm getting a lot of requests for comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.66,0:40:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的個人行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I acted on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.05,0:40:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力配合司法部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I will fully cooperate with the Justice Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.65,0:40:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼對外說嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can put that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.45,0:40:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.54,0:40:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這或許會吸引更多注意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It might generate more interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.69,0:40:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意我  而不是副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}On me. Not the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼情況我都能處理好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can handle whatever comes my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.02,0:40:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.69,0:40:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去把最新的剪報都打出來  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll print you out the most recent clips, too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.23,0:40:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想辦法對付鄧巴嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should I find a way to tip off Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.42,0:40:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是順其自然吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let nature take its course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.63,0:40:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛找到雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We got a hold of Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.66,0:40:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛回來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He just got back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.64,0:40:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.49,0:40:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你的安保隊都安排好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've arranged everything with your detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.86,0:40:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好  道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've done good work, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.65,0:40:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.63,0:41:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}菲茨
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.19,0:41:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  這樣好多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There. That's much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.20,0:41:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.97,0:41:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.89,0:41:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我有點喝醉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I'm a little drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.25,0:41:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是你家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.02,0:41:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以隨心所欲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.94,0:41:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也該喝一杯酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should have a glass of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.64,0:42:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  夫人  但是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I appreciate that, ma'am, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.15,0:42:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經下班了  對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're off your shift, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.09,0:42:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.64,0:42:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不許說不喝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I won't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.21,0:42:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該把好東西浪費在我身上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, you shouldn't waste any of your good stuff on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.39,0:42:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其實根本不懂品酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't really know anything about wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.19,0:42:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那喝點波本威士忌怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then how about bourbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.74,0:42:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定想喝一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I bet you like a little of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.76,0:42:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然不介意能喝點波本威士忌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I definitely don't mind a bourbon from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.33,0:42:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就喝波本威士忌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then bourbon it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.94,0:42:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在很難找啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're a tough man to track down these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.53,0:42:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到手錶了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You got the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.02,0:42:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變則善\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"To improve is to change."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.06,0:42:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常變則至善\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"To perfect is to change often."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.59,0:42:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你想要什麼樣的變化呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What sort of change are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.78,0:42:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我有選擇餘地的變化\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whichever leaves me options.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.46,0:42:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在格蘭頓-希爾遇到麻煩了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Trouble at Glendon Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.26,0:43:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶薪休假  直到調查結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Paid leave till the investigation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.89,0:43:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少是帶薪的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, at least you're being paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.81,0:43:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是終止我合夥人身份的第一步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}First step in terminating my partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.98,0:43:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你也懂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know how things go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.06,0:43:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是我洗不掉的汙點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there's a stain I can't wash out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.54,0:43:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你在尋找就業機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you're looking for career opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.50,0:43:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是要把自己整個賣給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not offering myself to you wholesale.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.61,0:43:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續跟你鬥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I keep fighting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.61,0:43:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是力度會小一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I can fight you less.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.99,0:43:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說"小一點"的意思是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And by "less" you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.70,0:43:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你痛  但不會讓你完蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Enough to hurt, but not finish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.14,0:43:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為回報  我在格蘭頓-希爾之外也有前途\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And in return I have a future beyond Glendon Hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.59,0:43:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼樣的前途\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whatever that might look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.78,0:43:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你是要保持中立\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you offer neutrality,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.24,0:43:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但最終會追隨勝利者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you'll go with the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.36,0:43:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看著更厲害的人獲勝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I figure let the best man win.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.67,0:43:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你失敗了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you go down,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.47,0:43:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會是因為我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it won't be because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.71,0:43:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這已經挺夠意思了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.26,0:43:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where is this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.29,0:43:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保險  沒別的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Insurance. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.30,0:43:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這跟傑姬有關嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does it have anything to do with Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.50,0:43:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.67,0:44:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你已經收服了博奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you've got Birch in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.28,0:44:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會選擇烏麥克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Womack's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.45,0:44:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們太親密了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.22,0:44:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是傑奎琳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But Jacqueline...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.55,0:44:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這單純是關於我的前途\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is about my future, pure and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.19,0:44:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's not a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.86,0:44:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著這塊表吧  就當做誠意的象徵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keep the watch, as a token of good faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.78,0:44:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他雖然否認  但他在保護她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He might deny it, but he's protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.61,0:44:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有意識到的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What he doesn't realize is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.04,0:44:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比雷蒙德更不在乎傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have even less regard for Jackie than Raymond does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.36,0:44:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Poor Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.79,0:44:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感情用事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The heart can choke the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.25,0:44:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理智就會受到影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when all its blood flows back unto itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.99,0:45:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說"我不喜歡深色頭發的女孩"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said, "I don't like brunettes."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.21,0:45:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我差點錯過了派對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Looks like I almost missed the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.19,0:45:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下班了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm off the clock, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.36,0:45:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張  弗蘭西斯  我打破了一個杯子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, relax. Francis, I broke a glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.21,0:45:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華被一塊碎片割傷了手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and Edward cut his hand on a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.42,0:45:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.35,0:45:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得給你換繃帶了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.54,0:46:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那個解下來  我去拿新的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take that off, and I'll get fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.56,0:46:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望您不要介意  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hope you don't mind, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.68,0:46:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下了班...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was off-duty --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.56,0:46:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is she, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.66,0:46:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了嗎  有一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Drunk? A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.45,0:46:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喝了多少這東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many of these have you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.61,0:46:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝了一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A few.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.32,0:46:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止一點吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More than a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.07,0:46:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以用你的杯子嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.43,0:46:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.40,0:46:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.60,0:46:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況還行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.56,0:46:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流了很多血\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.91,0:46:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看上去那麼糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Looks worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.76,0:46:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.28,0:46:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝了酒不那麼痛了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The bourbon helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.09,0:47:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果痛你就說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now you let me know if this hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.77,0:47:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不痛  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not one bit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.54,0:49:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你頭痛嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.53,0:49:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.57,0:49:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡前吃了幾片阿司匹林\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Took a few aspirin before I went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.20,0:49:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.37,0:50:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡得可香了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I slept like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.00,0:50:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  你需要好好睡一覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good. You needed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.35,0:50:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.11,0:50:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.14,0:50:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個地址老是出現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This one address keeps popping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.62,0:50:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.39,0:50:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.36,0:50:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Morning, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.57,0:50:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Morning, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.27,0:50:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是美好的一天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a beautiful day.
